title: Sunfly SF264 & SFMW896 Latest Karaoke CDG Feb 2008
description:
Hi Folks,
Here&#039;s the new Sunfly discs, hot off the press.
I am still taking requests for the next Sunfly Most Wanted release, so leave your suggestions here. Obvious hits have more chance than weird indie tracks.  Voting for someone elses suggestion will give it more chance too.
Thanks to all of you who looked at my wifes new perfume business and congratulations to the many who decided to take it on, and who are now making some handy extra cash. What amazed me most of all was the international effect, as my wife has now inroduced people in 7 different countries. For those who asked, virtually any country can join in, even Russia, Italy and Belgium have now started up.

To see a picture of my wife go to www.newsmells.info

On this disc I can take the blame for tracks 1,3,7,8,9 and 15 although in a couple of cases they just did another track by the same band, for example I actually requested "Shine a little love" by ELO and "Pure & Easy" by The Who.

It is nice to see loads of you are uploading new karaoke material all the time, keep up the fantastic work. Remember to put the word Karaoke in the Torrent name, so we can find it. I am still looking for stuff on the Sing to the World label and we could do with some more vcd and dvd stuff.

If anyone else wants to take a look at the wifes perfume business you can find it at newsmells.com and .info

I look forward to your karaoke requests. Let&#039;s see some real crackers.

EzeRoss
